        Parameters:
        action - the action done by the agent
        round - the current round number
        turn - the turn within the round
        time - the time, running from t = 0 (start) to t = 1 (deadline). The time is normalized, so agents need not be concerned with the actual internal clock.
        parties - the discounted utils of the parties
        agreed - the agreement Bid that the parties agreed on , or null if no agreement yet.
